OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy start
OL,6,Facross Shetland with patchy rain,
OL,7,Fdrier and brighter in Orkney with a
OL,8,Fscattering of showers. Becoming drier
OL,9,Fwith brightening skies in Shetland,
OL,10,Falthough still the chance of the odd
OL,11,Fshower. Easing winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBright with a scattering of
OL,14,Fshowers this evening, then mainly dry
OL,15,Facross Shetland overnight. Thickening
OL,16,Fcloud and patchy rain pushing into
OL,17,FOrkney later in the night. Winds
OL,18,Fmostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
