OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FIt will be mostly cloudy with
OL,6,Frain or showers, but drier and
OL,7,Fbrighter across Shetland during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Winds light or moderate from
OL,9,Fthe east or southeast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Monday with sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Windy with rain giving way to
OL,14,Fshowers on Tuesday. Occasional showers
OL,15,Fon Wednesday with easing winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
